Package: quantlab
Title: High-Speed Strategy Tester
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Truong Giang", "Do", email = "giangh14cqt@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")), person("Jan", "Melan", role = "aut"), person("Sebastian", "Chmielewski", role = "aut"))
Author: Truong Giang Do, Jan Melan, Sebastian Chmielewski
Maintainer: Truong Giang Do <giangh14cqt@gmail.com>
Description: A high-speed backtesting framework for R, utilizing R6 for state 
    management and Rcpp for performance-critical path-dependent simulations. 
    It provides a modular structure for testing simple trading strategies on 
    historical market data, specifically optimized for Polish market assets.
